# ESLint Plugin - LLM-Optimized Message Format

You are working in the @forge-js/eslint-plugin package. When creating or modifying ESLint rule messages, ALWAYS follow the 4-line LLM-optimized format.

## Format Standard

Every error/warning message MUST have exactly 4 lines:

```
Line 1: [Icon] [Issue Name] (CWE-XXX) | [Severity]
Line 2:    ‚ùå Current: [Bad practice example]
Line 3:    ‚úÖ Fix: [Solution with pattern]
Line 4:    üìö [Documentation link or context]
```

