## Implementation Template

```typescript
messages: {
  ruleName:
    '[ICON] [Issue Name] (CWE-XXX) | [SEVERITY]\n' +
    '   ‚ùå Current: [bad example]\n' +
    '   ‚úÖ Fix: [good solution]\n' +
    '   üìö [link or context]',
}
```

## DO's ‚úÖ

- Include CWE references
- Use 4 lines with newlines (\n)
- Include both bad example AND fix
- Provide actionable solutions
- Link to documentation
- Use correct severity level
- Indent lines 2-4 with 3 spaces
- Use emoji for visual scanning
- Test on playground app

## DON'Ts ‚ùå

- Skip CWE references
- Use vague examples
- Provide only problems
- Mix unrelated concepts
- Create biased rules
- Add special-case logic
- Forget severity/icon
- Skip documentation

